Version Date: 1997-05-16Version Text: 1997-05-16 Subject: null  Type: null  Notes: LRECL with SAS and SPSS setup files (for Wave I only);Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: (1) This data collection includes an updated version  of Wave I data (nine invalid cases were deleted, a small number of  respondent sex codes were changed, and changes were made to the  documentation), as well as the addition of previously unreleased Wave  II data from the survey, representing the complete National Survey of  Families and Households. As such, it supersedes the Wave I data that  were released in the NATIONAL SURVEY OF FAMILIES AND HOUSEHOLDS,  1987-1988 (ICPSR 6041). (2) Two percent of the interviews were  conducted in Spanish. (3) The skip maps are available only in hardcopy  form upon request from ICPSR. (4) Lists of additional related  publications and papers are contained in the codebook documentation.  (5) This ICPSR release of the NSFH consists of the March 1997 version  of this data collection. (6) Users of the NSFH data should consult the   NSFH website at http://www.ssc.wisc.edu/nsfh
<a href="http://www.ssc.wisc.edu/nsfh">http://www.ssc.wisc.edu/nsfh</a>
to check for periodic  updates of the data. The website also offers a bibliography, working  papers, and other information about NSFH. Users may also contact the ICPSR resource person for this site at resource@icpsr.umich.edu.; Subject: null  Type: null  Notes: Data file(s), and electronic documentation.;
